                ("Time and Work", "A machine P can print one lakh books in 8 hours, machine Q in 10 hours and machine R in 12 hours. All the machines are started at 9 A.M. while machine P is closed at 11 A.M. and the remaining two machines complete the work. Approximately at what time will the work (to print one lakh books) be finished?", "11:30 A.M.", "12 noon", "12:30 P.M.", "1:00 P.M.", "D", "Work in 2 hrs: 2(1/8+1/10+1/12) = ... Rem work done by Q+R. Total time approx 1pm."),
                ("Time and Work", "A can finish a work in 18 days and B can do the same work in 15 days. B worked for 10 days and left the job. In how many days, A alone can finish the remaining work?", "5", "5 1/2", "6", "8", "C", "B done 10/15=2/3. Rem 1/3. A takes 1/3 * 18 = 6 days."),
